results.deck: A Japanese RPG developer primarily responsible for the Tales series as well as the early Megami Tensei games.
results.description:
Overview

Wolf Team was a Japanese developer of RPGs that is mostly known for Namco's Tales series. The company was also responsible for the first two Megami Tensei titles. A rift between Wolf Team and Namco formed during the development of Tales of Phantasia, and key members of Wolf Team left to form tri-Ace. In 2003, Namco merged Wolf Team into Namco Tales Team.
